    <item>
      <title>官员称中国青年失业率上升值得关注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/china-s-rising-youth-unemployment-needs-attention-official-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位政府官员警告说，中国不断上升的青年失业率需要更多的审查，因为疲软的劳动力市场继续拖累世界第二大经济体的增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/china-s-rising-youth-unemployment-needs-attention-official-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 06:18:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>BP 专注于熟悉的领域，竞争对手则开拓新的石油勘探领域</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/bp-focuses-on-familiar-turf-in-gulf-of-mexico-as-rivals-push-new-oil-frontiers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[对于一家以从伊朗到阿拉斯加的前沿石油发现而闻名的公司来说，英国石油公司显然没有出现在当今最热门的新石油公司中。该公司的勘探和生产主管对此表示同意。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/bp-focuses-on-familiar-turf-in-gulf-of-mexico-as-rivals-push-new-oil-frontiers</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝莱德表示美联储很难大幅降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-16/blackrock-says-hard-for-fed-to-cut-rates-aggressively-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝莱德副主席Philipp Hildebrand表示，美联储今年可能会降息一两次，但服务业通胀仍然很高，很难达到央行2%的目标。他在“彭博市场：亚洲”上发表演讲。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-16/blackrock-says-hard-for-fed-to-cut-rates-aggressively-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 05:45:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
