      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/stocks-look-more-vulnerable-in-asia-than-peers-on-fed-re-pricing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周二亚洲股市的大幅抛售凸显了人们对该地区在利率上升和地缘政治紧张局势加剧的情况下脆弱性的担忧。]]></description>
